          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>The Anti-Deficiency Reform and Enforcement Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill strengthens penalties for federal employees who violate the Anti-Deficiency Act. Additionally, the bill authorizes an agency to award a cash payment to an employee who discloses a potential violation of the Anti-Deficiency Act. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-09-25T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
